Package edu.cmu.commons.collections.trie

Interface Summary
NavigableTrie<E,V>  
NavigableTrieNode<E,V>  
Trie<E,V> Trie extends Map<List<E>,V> where keys are represented in a compact data structure (key sequences share common prefixes).
TrieIterator<E,V> A depth-first iterator for Tries.
TrieIterator.Visitor<E,V> A class which encapsulates various call-backs which may occur during iteration over a Trie.
TrieNode<E,V> Basic contract for nodes used to build Tries.
TrieNodeInvocationHandler<E,V> InvocationHandler used when proxying TrieNodes.
 

Class Summary
HashTrie<E,V> Trie implementation using HashTrieNodes internally.
HashTrieNode<E,V> TrieNode implementation using HashMap internally.
TreeTrie<E,V> Trie implementation using TreeTrieNodes internally.
TreeTrieNode<E,V> NavigableTrieNode implementation using TreeMap internally.
TrieNodeValueDecorator<E,V> TrieNodeInvocationHandler which supports TrieNode value property.
